properties.name: betweenEndText
properties.description: Specifies the null text for the editor that sets the end of a range for the "between" filter operation.

properties.name: betweenStartText
properties.description: Specifies the null text for the editor that sets the start of a range for the "between" filter operation.

properties.name: operationDescriptions
properties.description: Specifies descriptions for filter operations in the filter list.

properties.name: showAllText
properties.description: Specifies text for the "All" filter operation.

properties.name: showOperationChooser
properties.description: Specifies whether to display filter icons.

properties.name: visible
properties.description: Specifies whether the filter row is visible.
